    adms:representationTechnique <http://purl.org/adms/representationtechnique/SKOS> ;
    dcat:contactPoint <https://w3id.org/italia/data/contact-point/ISTAT-NDC> ;
    dcat:distribution <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/data/StateProperty/distribution/destinazione-di-uso-CSV>,
        <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/data/StateProperty/distribution/destinazione-di-uso-JSON-LD>,
        <https://w3id.org/italia/real-estate/data/StateProperty/distribution/destinazione-di-uso-RDF-Turtle>,
